(180 Degree Longitude Passes Through Us)

363
00:29:09,088 --> 00:29:11,400
Let's do something fun.

364
00:29:11,400 --> 00:29:12,355
What is?

365
00:29:12,422 --> 00:29:13,333
A game.

366
00:29:13,333 --> 00:29:18,200
This game is called 'tell the truth'.

367
00:29:20,888 --> 00:29:25,577
(180 Degree Longitude Passes Through Us)

368
00:29:28,466 --> 00:29:32,377
Come here. Sit here now.

369
00:29:32,377 --> 00:29:37,511
But before we begin,
you need a blindfold.

370
00:29:39,911 --> 00:29:42,533
What surprise do you have for me?

371
00:29:42,688 --> 00:29:44,977
I'm so eager to know my heart is beating so fast.

372
00:29:44,977 --> 00:29:46,733
What if I get a heart attack?

373
00:29:46,822 --> 00:29:47,666
Are you for real?

374
00:29:47,933 --> 00:29:50,666
Let me listen if your heart is still beating.

375
00:29:50,666 --> 00:29:51,622
What if it isn't?

376
00:29:52,333 --> 00:29:53,377
Stop being silly, Wang.

377
00:29:53,488 --> 00:29:57,555
Wait a minute. Get ready for your surprise.

378
00:29:57,644 --> 00:29:58,755
Sit still.

379
00:30:04,177 --> 00:30:05,511
Don't cheat.

380
00:30:15,800 --> 00:30:17,333
Can I take the blindfold off?

381
00:30:17,444 --> 00:30:19,844
Not yet. Don't rush. It won't be long now.

